Data Objects Loaded by load_general_data()

Source: R/data.R
afsetools-data.Rd

This package contains 73+ data objects that are loaded into the environment when you call load_general_data(). These include nomenclatures, biomass coefficients, global warming potentials, and other parameters needed for environmental footprint calculations.

Details

The data objects include:

  • 35 nomenclature and classification objects

  • 17 biomass coefficient objects

  • 7 global warming potential objects

  • 3 biological nitrogen fixation objects

  • 6 constants and scalars

  • Color palettes and utility vectors

For complete documentation of all data objects, see the DATA_REFERENCE.md file in the package repository, or use ?object_name for specific objects after loading them with load_general_data().
